# NLC Technical Documentation

[Connect](https://connect.nationalleadership.gov.uk/) is run on Amazon Web Services (AWS) Elastic Kubernetes Service (EKS). It consists of multiple components which ensure the running of the system.

The following documenation has the following priorities:

1. High level overview of the infrastructure
2. Break down of each components
3. Runbooks
4. Other useful information

The aim of this documenation is to provide an overview of the NLC Connect infrastructure and a helpful jumping off point for implementing your own EKS setup.